{"tid":427844,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"已知曹星如點解贏-有相","createTime":"2017-10-07T16:19:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T13:47:46.000Z","uid":54373,"like":16,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"deb4a637ed79f5695164ba4fd01980fe7e4ec059","tid":427844,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:19:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171007/s00001/aa904bbee9553e92fae4936fa825cafe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171007%2Fs00001%2Faa904bbee9553e92fae4936fa825cafe.jpg&h=e5a90e99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拳壇「神奇小子」曹星如（Rex）在今晚王者對決，迎來職業生涯最難打的前世界冠軍河野公平。到第6回合，曹星如左眼腫得不能張開，拳證決定中止比賽，判定Rex以點數取勝。只見曹星如賽後左眼重創紅腫如雞蛋，連經理人都稱擔心其骨折，如此情況，民建聯立法會議員葛珮帆依然可以捉到曹星如合照，認真唔簡單。"},{"pid":"561a6d406e565a0496ff52b9886b62784392505c","tid":427844,"uid":54373,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:19:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如此情況，民建聯立法會議員葛珮帆依然可以捉到曹星如合照，認真唔簡單。</span>"},{"pid":"a6951a5291b4281fde4fb7e1f16a8d8139e3d3b0","tid":427844,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:39:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ead87e526297837d6493b5fd5fd7ea62e379d2e1","tid":427844,"uid":81037,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:41:51.000Z","msg":"Rex收左共產黨幾多錢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d39d84b5154f09db2251a5252af310773c09eaa","tid":427844,"uid":34444,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:44:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Rex收左共產黨幾多錢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又可以捱多陣 咬廣告費過日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79eb0a3cf3ffb61716096666ce5d99c97f4531e4","tid":427844,"uid":33125,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20